Titolo: DragonBox

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: DragonBox is an educational game series developed and published by WeWantToKnow AS, a Norwegian studio. DragonBox Algebra was released on May 9, 2012 for iOS. It was created to teach children math, such as algebra.
The game won a 2016 Games For Change award for "Best Learning Game", and received positive reception from critics, who praised the efficacy of the app.